verbose_text: GFP + neurons birth dated with RV-GFP in SAMP8 mice 2 days after CORT pellet removal showed increased dendritic complexity and spine density, with immature spines (thin, stubby) specifically increased, which were seemingly opposite in SAMR1 mice of the same age.
